name: SOS-9045-04
description:
Welcome to The SOS-9045 visual illusion project. SOS-9045 is a collection based on Symmetry, Order, Square geometry, 90 and 45 degree angles.
Each piece of this collection is presented in 1:1 dimensions. Maximum black and white contrast, repetitive rhythm and increasing or decreasing wavelength in this collection has created a visual illusion and the Order and Harmony of the components of each piece creates a sense of visual satisfaction in you.
So become a member of the big SOS-9045 family by buying nfts from this collection. Limited Versions!
